Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b435dc3197dde5bb83f910531314868352502d4","tid":2439109,"uid":250039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T01:18:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28368b1391a5afa60cf3c97aaa1fe0003426b65f","tid":2439109,"uid":310867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T10:34:03.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d33cf92fdef0176f5d45e507ddf299354584561f","tid":2439109,"uid":106950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T19:52:38.000Z","msg":"幾正喎 大佛普拉斯都好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bb4d200f4dfc35465220dc13876373a27c832e1","tid":2439109,"uid":231596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T20:37:42.000Z","msg":"中意劉冠廷同王彩樺"},{"pid":"f619753e890c694f6b5584d8b0bd71f3ee522d53","tid":2439109,"uid":250039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d33cf92fdef0176f5d45e507ddf299354584561f","tid":2439109,"uid":106950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T19:52:38.000Z","msg":"幾正喎 大佛普拉斯都好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T09:07:41.000Z","msg":"因為麥娜我都再睇返大佛。始終大佛好似再好少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}